@endnode

@node "Compiler" "Compiler"
@{b}@{u}Compiler@{ub}@{uu}

YCrCb was written and compiled using CED V3.5 and SAS/C 6.55 on an Amiga
4000/040. YCrCb should perform equally well on any Amiga.

@endnode

@node "Bugs" "Bugs"
@{b}@{u}Bugs@{ub}@{uu}

* Cannot load files saved with Colour Kill turned on in the Proc Amp window.

@endnode

